Title: An Act Changing the Name of Barangay Salvador Poblacion in the Municipality of Salvador, Province of Lanao Del Norte, to Barangay Balimbing
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 684
An Act Changing the Name of Barangay Salvador Poblacion in the Municipality of Salvador, Province of Lanao Del Norte, to Barangay Balimbing
Section 1. The name of Barangay Salvador Poblacion in the Municipality of Salvador, Province of Lanao del Norte, is changed to Barangay Balimbing.1a\^/phi1
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: March 7, 1984
